# """
# NS-FPN + FGLA + StableBDDMv2
# ============================
#
# This is a single-file architecture implementation designed to plug directly
# into the user's train.py.
#
# Key replacements
# ----------------
# 1. LFP / wav_Enhance path:
#    - replaced by FGLA block family (pure PyTorch)
#
# 2. Previous unstable BDDM / PSA_MLLABlock-like path:
#    - replaced by the user-provided StableBDDMv2
#    - used inside the top-down fusion wrapper for safer feature propagation
#
# Design goals
# ------------
# - runnable in a normal PyTorch environment
# - stable feature propagation
# - explicit Conv + Norm + Act
# - residual design
# - FFN path preserved
# - no custom CUDA ops required
# """
