# This is a single-file architecture implementation designed to plug directly
# into the user's train.py.
#
# Key replacements
# ----------------
# 1. Original FGLA/LFP path:
#    - replaced by WSGALFP / WSGALFPStage
#
# 2. Original PSA_MLLABlock-like compatibility path:
#    - replaced by CBSASFS
#    - top-down cross-level fusion also uses CBSASFS
#
# Design goals
# ------------
# - runnable in a normal PyTorch environment
# - stable feature propagation
# - explicit Conv + Norm + Act
# - residual design
# - FFN path preserved
# - no custom CUDA ops required
# """
