# """
# NS-FPN + W_PSA + SP_SKmod_HFMD (high-precision stable version)
# ===============================================================
#
# This file is designed to plug directly into the user's existing train.py.
#
# Key points
# ----------
# 1. Keep the NS-FPN overall encoder-decoder structure compatible with the user's pipeline.
# 2. Replace the original LFP-style enhancement with W_PSA.
# 3. Replace the original SFS-style top-down cross-scale fusion with SP_SKmod_HFMD.
# 4. Embed KANLinear directly in this file so there is no extra dependency on external kan.py.
# 5. Bias the design toward higher accuracy while still keeping essential stabilizers.
# """
#
