#
# """
# SCSegamba + CBSA replacement
# ============================
#
# This file is a train.py-friendly, single-file adaptation of SCSegamba.
#
# What is kept from the original repository:
# - ConvPatchEmbed stem style
# - SAVSS backbone layout (4 stacked SAVSS_Layer blocks)
# - GBC, PAF, DySample, MFS decoder chain
# - decoder/head style and multi-scale fusion logic
#
# What is replaced:
# - The original SAVSS_2D selective scan / SASS scan path depended on
#   mamba_ssm selective_scan_fn and CUDA/Triton extensions.
# - Here it is replaced with a pure PyTorch CBSA-style contract-and-broadcast
#   attention core so the model can run without mamba-ssm.
#
# Notes:
# - This is not the official SCSegamba training stack from mmcls/mmcv.
# - It is a practical single-file architecture designed to plug directly into
#   the user's existing archs.py + train.py workflow.
# """
#
#
# # =========================================================
# # Utility blocks
# # =========================================================
