#
# # ============================================================
# # SegFormer single-file adaptation
# #
# # Core structure follows the official NVlabs SegFormer repository:
# # - MixVisionTransformer backbone (mix_transformer.py)
# # - SegFormerHead decoder (segformer_head.py)
# #
# # Minimal changes for the user's unified training framework:
# # - direct tensor input: x -> model(x)
